    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid project or a budget-friendly daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable paint fading on the roof and a few minor dents along the passenger side. Inside, the upholstery has some visible staining and a small tear in the driver's seat. Mechanically, it runs and drives, though it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s an honest car that reflects its history and is priced accordingly.",
